                     <p>The letters are small to medium size separately made without ligatures. The middle stroke of epsilon sometimes is extended and joins the following letter. There is no great difference regarding the breadth of the letters epsilon, theta, omicron and sigma . The text was written after the papyrus was turned 180 degress regarding the recto side.</p>
